data.description: OFFERING POSSIBLE UP TO $6000 IN CLOSING COSTS FOR ACCEPTABLE OFFER.  This Duplex is conveniently located close to shopping, schools and employers, near William Cannon and Menchaca.  Duplex is on a quiet street with trees. Each unit is well appointed, having 2 bedrooms (up); 1.5 bathS.  Each has a full 1 car garage with separate lockable storage between units and garage.  Each has private fenced and gated back yard.  Private patio-deck for A side and private covered patio and deck on the B side. Each yard has trees that provide shaded area for occupants to enjoy.  Lot next door owned by City of Austin, so green area.  Kitchens each have pantry and built in laundry closets.  Each has disposal, electric stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, washer and dryer included.   Kit and LR have tile flooring with vinyl laminate flooring upstairs and carpet on stairs; wood burning fireplaces in LR.  Primary bedrooms each have 2 ample closets.  Storage under stairs.  Balconies have views of trees.  Photos are of units when vacant prior to being leased.  See documents for list of many upgrades, repairs etc. completed recently.
